{"tid":942617,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下班習慣先聞臭襪才洗　福建男染肺真菌病入院","createTime":"2018-12-16T01:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T05:25:08.000Z","uid":222618,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb3521a2b3db2ae6e50543f7b42b412e4960120","tid":942617,"uid":222618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"漳州第909醫院呼吸結核科醫生麥轉英表示，彭姓事主因持續一周咳嗽及胸悶不適求醫，醫生根據檢查影像，起初診斷為普通肺炎。但治療一個多星期後，事主情况反而惡化，醫生再為他進行穿刺檢查，證實他患上肺真菌病。<br />\n<br />\n麥轉英指，事主本身健康良好，生活環境亦乾淨，但他有個癖好，<span style=\"color: red;\">下班總要先聞過襪子，才將臭襪拿去洗</span>。麥表示，有腳癬的人鞋襪易滋生真菌，懷疑事主的「聞襪」習慣，加上近期要熬夜照顧幼兒，令抵抗力下降，導致真菌感染。<br />\n<br />\n麥指出，肺真菌病治療費用貴，且病情發展非常迅速，若不及時發現，「死亡率還是挺高的」；但若及時發現並確認真菌種類，對症下藥，「通常治療效果還是不錯」。事主經治療後，目前康復進展良好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7712fd3480557c09a33fedbf29d2060f3cb184a0","tid":942617,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"呢篇文係咪要警告啲腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b478e80d0e7414c09e04a943f53c8ab864b8ac3","tid":942617,"uid":222618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7712fd3480557c09a33fedbf29d2060f3cb184a0","tid":942617,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"呢篇文係咪要警告啲腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" c